e=\"display:none\"\n    src=\"https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=1756982567959907&ev=PageView&noscript=1\"\n  /></noscript>\n  <!-- End Facebook Pixel Code -->\n\n\n   <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n   <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=0\">\n\n   <!-- Bootstrap -->\n   <link href=\"..//page/css/bootstrap.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n   <link href=\"..//page/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n   <!-- Custom styles for this template -->\n   <link href=\"..//page/css/cross-code.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n  <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js for IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->\n  <!-- WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file:// -->\n  <!--[if lt IE 9]>\n    <script src=\"https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js\"></script>\n  <![endif]-->\n\n</head>\n<body class=\"home\">\n    <nav class=\"navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top\" role=\"navigation\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"social\">\n          <a class=\"twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/RadicalFishGame\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Twitter</span></a>\n          <a class=\"facebook\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/RadicalFishGames\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Facebook</span></a>\n          <a class=\"tumblr\" href=\"http://radicalfishgames.tumblr.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Tumblr</span></a>\n          <a class=\"indiedb\" href=\"http://www.indiedb.com/games/crosscode\" target=\"_blank\"><span>IndieDB</span></a>\n          <a class=\"youtube\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/radicalfishgames\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Youtube</span></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n          <button type=\"button\" class=\"navbar-toggle collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#navbar\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"navbar\">\n            <span class=\"sr-only\">Toggle navigation</span>\n            <span class=\"icon-bar\"></span>\n            <span class=\"icon-bar\"></span>\n            <span class=\"icon-bar\"></span>\n          </button>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"navbar\" class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\">\n          <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav\">\n            <li><a href=\"#play\">Play</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#download\">Download</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"http://crosscode.gamepedia.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Wiki</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"http://forum.cross-code.com\">Forum</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"http://www.radicalfishgames.com\">Blog</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            <li class=\"optional\"><a href=\"http://www.radicalfishgames.com/presskit/sheet.php?p=crosscode\" target=\"_blank\">Presskit</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n\n      </div>\n    </nav>\n\n\n    <section class=\"play\" id=\"play\" style=\"background-position: center -120px;\">\n\n        <div class=\"lea\" id=\"lea\" style=\"background-position: center 0px;\"></div>\n\n        <div class=\"scanlines\"></div>\n\n        <h1><span>CrossCode</span></h1>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n\n\n          <div class=\"blackbox video\">\n            <div><iframe id=\"ytplayer\" type=\"text/html\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bzZ3gB9RcIc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"blackbox cta\">\n              <div>\n                <p>Play the Demo</p>\n                <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/368340/\" target=\"_blank\">Steam</a>\n                <a href=\"start\" target=\"_blank\">Web Version</a>\n                <p>Get the Game</p>\n                <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/368340/\" target=\"_blank\">Steam</a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/crosscode-switch/\" target=\"_blank\">Nintendo Switch</a>\n                <a href=\"https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0895-CUSA15452_00-CROSSCODEPLAYSTA\" target=\"_blank\">Playstation 4</a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/de-de/p/crosscode/9n04rqq64524?rtc=1\" target=\"_blank\">Xbox One</a>\n              </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div><!-- /.container -->\n        <!--\n        <div class=\"steamBox blackbox\" >\n          <div>\n            <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/368340/\" target=\"_blank\" ><img src=\"..//page/img/banner-early-access.png\" /></a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        -->\n\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"features\">\n        <span class=\"anchor\" id=\"about\"></span>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"summary\">\n                 <h2>A retro-inspired <b>2D Action RPG</b> set in the <b>distant future</b></h2>\n                <p class=\"summary\">\n                    Meet <b>Lea</b> as she logs into an <b>MMO of the distant future</b>.<br>\n                    Follow her steps as she discovers a vast world, meets other players and\n                    overcomes all the challenges of the game.\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    Also: <b>Lea can't speak</b>. Nope, no heroic mime. She is <b>actually mute</b>.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"featureList\">\n                <div class=\"feature\">\n                    <img src=\"..//page/img/feature-story.png\" title=\"Such sci-fi computing.\">\n                    <p>A story about the distant future of gaming - from an unexpected angle. Plenty of characters and plot twists included.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature\">\n                    <img src=\"..//page/img/feature-balls.png\" title=\"A very roundabout way to hit a switch!\">\n                    <p>Master the bouncing ball mechanics and solve a whole bunch of puzzles. </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature\">\n                    <img src=\"..//page/img/feature-combat-2.png\" title=\"More damage numbers are better.\">\n                    <p>\n                        CrossCode has fast, action-packed combat filled with damage numbers.\n                        And we still managed to squeeze some strategy in there!\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature\">\n                    <img src=\"..//page/img/feature-elements.png\" title=\"The Heat element also comes with big explosions.\">\n                    <p>\n                        Be a proper avatar and master all 4 elements: Cold, Heat, Shock and Wave.\n                        What, those are not the right elements? No idea what you are talking about.\n\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature\">\n                    <img src=\"..//page/img/feature-rpg.png\" title=\"Gotta get this defense.\">\n                    <p>\n                        Being a proper RPG, CrossCode comes with tons of skills, equipment, items, NPCs,\n                        quests and all those fun little things consuming your precious time.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature\">\n                    <img src=\"..//page/img/feature-awesome.png\" title=\"Hit its weak point for massive damage!\">\n                    <p>\n                        CrossCode is full of awesome: huge hostile cyborg crabs, a seaman with a jetpack and\n                        head-banging meerkats.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"more\" id=\"more\" style=\"background-position: left -1463px;\">\n         <div class=\"moreInner\">\n\n             <div class=\"characters\" id=\"characters\" style=\"background-position: center 548.5px;\"></div>\n\n              <div class=\"blackbox download\">\n                <div>\n                    <span class=\"anchor\" id=\"download\"></span>\n                    <h2>Download</h2>\n                    <p>You can also play the <b>CrossCode Demo</b> offline, outside of the Browser.</p>\n                    <a href=\"http://www.cross-code.com/release/crosscode-demo.zip\" class=\"biggerButton\">CrossCode for Windows</a>\n                    <p>Linux and OSX demo available through <b>Steam</b></p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"blackbox support\">\n                <div>\n                  <span class=\"anchor\" id=\"support\"></span>\n                  <h2>Support Us</h2>\n                  <p>You can <b>spread the word</b> and follow us on:</p>\n                  <div class=\"social\">\n                    <a class=\"twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/RadicalFishGame\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Twitter</span></a>\n                    <a class=\"facebook\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/RadicalFishGames\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Facebook</span></a>\n                    <a class=\"tumblr\" href=\"http://radicalfishgames.tumblr.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Tumblr</span></a>\n                    <a class=\"indiedb\" href=\"http://www.indiedb.com/games/crosscode\" target=\"_blank\"><span>IndieDB</span></a>\n                    <a class=\"youtube\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/radicalfishgames\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Youtube</span></a>\n                  </div>\n                  <p>Or if you prefer E-Mail, subscribe to our <b>CrossCode News</b> mailinglist:</p>\n                  <!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->\n                  <div id=\"mc_embed_signup\">\n                  <form action=\"//radicalfishgames.us9.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=6990151f91beafabcd6d1da88&amp;id=d8b8c0320b\" method=\"post\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" name=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" class=\"validate\" target=\"_blank\" novalidate=\"\">\n                      <div id=\"mc_embed_signup_scroll\">\n                        <input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" class=\"email\" id=\"mce-EMAIL\" placeholder=\"email address\" required=\"\">\n                        <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->\n                        <div style=\"position: absolute; left: -5000px;\"><input type=\"text\" name=\"b_6990151f91beafabcd6d1da88_d8b8c0320b\" tabindex=\"-1\" value=\"\"></div>\n                        <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe\" name=\"subscribe\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe\" class=\"button\">\n                      </div>\n                  </form>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <!--End mc_embed_signup-->\n\n                  <p>And of course <a href=\"http://www.radicalfishgames.com\">visit our blog</a></p>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n         </div>\n    </section>\n\n\n    <section class=\"contact\" id=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <span class=\"anchor\" id=\"soundtrack\"></span>\n            <h2>Soundtrack</h2>\n            <iframe style=\"border: 0; width: 350px; height: 786px;\" src=\"https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=789187561/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=0687f5/transparent=true/\" seamless=\"\"><a href=\"http://interovgm.com/album/crosscode-original-game-soundtrack\">CrossCode (Original Game Soundtrack) by Deniz Akbulut</a></iframe>\n            <span class=\"anchor\" id=\"contact\"></span>\n            <h2>Contact</h2>\n            <p>Got feedback, bugs or just want to say hi? Send us a mail: <a href=\"mailto:feedback@radicalfishgames.com\">feedback@radicalfishgames.com</a></p>\n\n            <div class=\"imprint\">\n                <p>\n                  CrossCode.com © 2012 <a href=\"http://www.radicalfishgames.com\">Radical Fish Games</a>\n                  | <a href=\"http://www.radicalfishgames.com/presskit/sheet.php?p=crosscode\" target=\"_blank\">Presskit</a>\n                </p>\n\n                <p><b>Imprint</b><br>Radical Fish Games GmbH · Halbergstr 4 · 66121 Saarbrücken · Germany</p>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n    </section>\n\n    <script>\n\n        var isMobile = /Android|webOS|iPhone|iPad|iPod|BlackBerry|IEMobile|Opera Mini/i.test(navigator.userAgent);\n\n        if(!isMobile){\n            var bgScrollStart = -120, bgScrollFactor = 0.95,\n            leaScrollStart = 0, leaScrollFactor = 0.8,\n            moreScrollStart = 0, moreScrollFactor = 0.85,\n            charScrollFactor = 0.5;\n            function updateParallaxScroll(){\n                var scrollY = document.body.scrollTop || document.documentElement.scrollTop;\n                var bgValue = bgScrollStart + bgScrollFactor*scrollY;\n                $(\"#play\")[0].style.backgroundPosition = \"center \" + bgValue + \"px\";\n                var leaValue = leaScrollStart + leaScrollFactor*scrollY;\n                $(\"#lea\")[0].style.backgroundPosition = \"center \" + leaValue + \"px\";\n                var height = $(document).height();\n                moreScrollStart = -(height - $(\"#more\").height() - $(\"#footer\").height() - 150);\n                var moreValue = moreScrollStart + moreScrollFactor*scrollY;\n                $(\"#more\")[0].style.backgroundPosition = \"left \" + moreValue + \"px\";\n                var charOffset = $(\"#footer\").height() - 200;\n                var charValue = (document.body.scrollHeight - scrollY - window.innerHeight - charOffset)*charScrollFactor;\n                charValue = Math.max(0, charValue);\n                $(\"#characters\")[0].style.backgroundPosition = \"center \" + charValue + \"px\";\n            }\n            updateParallaxScroll();\n            $(document).scroll(updateParallaxScroll);\n            $(window).resize(updateParallaxScroll);\n            $(updateParallaxScroll);\n        }\n